const path = {
  HOME: "",
  PUBLIC: "/",
  LOGIN: "/login",
  REGISTER: "/register",
  PRODUCTS: "/products",
  BLOGS: "/blogs",
  OURSERVICES: "/our-services",
  FAQS: "/faqs",
  INTRODUCTE: "/intrordcude",
  NEWPAPER: "/newpaper",
  PRODUCT_DETAIL__ID__NAME: "/sanpham/:id/:name",
};

export default path;
